Introduction

Kyuri, also known as Kim Kyuri, is a South Korean singer-songwriter. She made her solo debut on November 28, 2022, with her first EP "Open The Door". She was a contestant on the JTBC survival show Girls On Fire and finished at rank 6 in the final round.
